I identified a concrete gap to patch: `source_id` frame-linked signals are currently ignored entirely, even when they deterministically encode `us-code-{title}-{section}-{digest}` and carry citation structure relevant to frame audits. I’m updating extraction to parse `source_id` into canonical title/section ontology terms (while still ignoring non-US-code IDs), then I’ll adjust/add tests and run the focused suite.
